  "texts": [
    "We reviewed work on synthetic images for VS tasks published from January 2014 to November 2023.",
    "We collected almost one hundred papers from the DBLP, 1 Scopus 2 and Web of Science 3 databases, using the following keywords: synthetic OR synthesis AND images AND computer vision AND video surveillance.",
    "We then selected publications from the following venues.",
    "In Sect. 3 we give a comprehensive overview of the VS applications mentioned above, focusing on issues that motivate the use of synthetic data.",
    "We then survey in Sect. 4 existing work on synthetic data for such applications, including a description of the techniques used to generate them."
